org.readlogsfirst.api.logreader.logsplitter
Interface LineSplittingStrategy

All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiLineLimitsSplitter, SingleLineSplittingStrategy
public interface LineSplittingStrategy

Strategy pattern that provide the parsing facility for log file lines. It is provided a set of lines coming from the log file and once the item is completed it composes the LogLine object and returns it
